unified-hnsw/
├── unified_hnsw.hpp          # Header file with declarations
├── unified_hnsw.cpp          # Implementation file
├── example_usage.cpp         # Example usage program
├── Makefile                  # Build configuration
├── README.md                 # Documentation (from earlier)
├── INSTALL.md               # Installation guide (from earlier)
├── EXAMPLES.md              # Usage examples (from earlier)
└── hnswlib/                 # HNSWlib directory (you need to add this)
    └── hnswlib/
        └── hnswlib.h


Complete Feature Set:
✅ Metrics: L2, IP, Cosine (L1 structure ready)
✅ Quantization: None (float), Binary, Ternary
✅ Binary Modes: STANDARD (median), BETTER (correlation-optimized)
✅ Rescoring: Optional with original vectors stored
✅ Epsilon Stop Condition: searchWithStopCondition(query, epsilon, min_cand, max_cand)
✅ SIMD Optimization: AVX2, AVX-512, ARM NEON
✅ Single File Storage: Everything in one file with magic header
✅ Stream-based I/O: Compatible with your modified HNSWlib
File Structure:
Each saved index contains (in order):

Magic header (0x484E5357)
Version number
Complete metadata
Quantizer thresholds (binary: 1 threshold/dim, ternary: 2 thresholds/dim)
Original vectors (if rescoring enabled)
HNSW graph structure
